To install the Adito LDAP authentication module, do the following:

* Run "ant install" in $ADITO_HOME
* Run "ant install" in this directory.
* Copy the build/release/adito-community-ldap.zip to $ADITO_HOME/adito/conf/repository/archives
* Re-run "ant install" in $ADITO_HOME
* Select LDAP for the user database in the install phase (see Installing and running Adito server in 
Wiki)
